<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.2.5">
<l>kōmaṅ kavaṅkak kaṭalvai yamuyyak kulamaṉ ṉaraṅkam maḻuviṟ ṟuṇiya,</l>
<l>tāmaṅ kamaruḷ paṭaitoṭ ṭaveṉṟit tavamā muṉiyait tamakkāk kakiṟpīr,</l>
<l>pūmaṅ kaitaṅkip pulamaṅ kaimaṉṉip pukaḻmaṅ kaiyeṅkun tikaḻap pukaḻcēr</l>
<l>cēmaṅ koḷpaimpūm poḻilcūḻn tatillait tiruccit rakūṭam ceṉṟucēr miṉkaḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who would make [as] your own the great sage of victorious tapas</l>
<l rend="indent">who used his weapon there on the battlefield</l>
<l>So that the bodies of the clan chiefs were cut with an axe</l>
<l rend="indent">and so that the kṣatriya perished, to save the earth with wavy seas,</l>
<l>Please go and gather at Tiruccitrakūṭam in Tillai</l>
<l rend="indent">surrounded by tranquil gardens of fresh flowers full of fame,</l>
<l>Since the lady of fame shines everywhere, [with] the lotus lady staying</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] lady earth enduring [there also].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
